Kent Sprouse was sentenced to death in 2004 for killing a police officer and a customer at a Texas gas station in 2002 . 
  Officer Harry Marvin 'Marty' Steinfeldt III was killed outside a convenience store in Ferris . 
  Sprouse also shot and killed customer Pedro Moreno at the gas station . 
  He will be executed by lethal injection on Thursday evening . 
 